---
title: Sesame-Crusted Haloumi & Chicken Burger with Beetroot Relish & Spiced Wedges
description: Serve up a hearty burger made with a golden "patty" of sesame-coated haloumi! A smear of dill-parsley mayo and sweet and tangy beetroot relish turns this veggie dinner into a taste sensation.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66d95f315a192a1abc1ee358-bee2d60b.jpeg
